加里","England":"英國","Castle Cary, Somersetshire, England":"英國薩默塞特卡素 加里","Devon, England":"英國戴文","lifeSummary":"當William de Cary於1230年出生在英國戴文時，他的父親John de Kary30歲，母親Elizabeth Stapleton21歲。他於1270年與Alicet Beaumont在英國英格蘭薩默塞特卡素 加里結婚。他們至少是3個兒子和1個女兒的父母。他在英國英格蘭戴文被列為lord of the manors of west polworth, paveston and karry。他去世於1303年在他的家鄉享年73歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1230–1303":"1230年–1303年","1240–1273":"1240年–1273年","1260–Female":"1260年–殁","1270–1304":"1270年–1304年","1272–Male":"1272年–殁","1273–Male":"1273年–殁","1200–1290":"1200年–1290年","1210–1231":"1210年–1231年","1231":"1231年","1230":"1230年","1273":"1273年","1240":"1240年","1272":"1272年","1260":"1260年","1270":"1270年","1290":"1290年","ABT 1260":"大约1260年","1304":"1304年","1303":"1303年","1259":"1259年","1200":"1200年","1210":"1210年","about 1231":"大约1231年","Somerset, England":"英国英格兰薩默塞特","Castle Cary,,,England":"英国英格兰薩默塞特卡素 加里","England":"英国","Castle Cary, Somersetshire, England":"英国薩默塞特卡素 加里","Devon, England":"英国戴文","lifeSummary":"当William de Cary于1230年出生在英国戴文时，他的父亲John de Kary30岁，母亲Elizabeth Stapleton21岁。他于1270年与Alicet Beaumont在英国英格兰薩默塞特卡素 加里结婚。他们至少是3个儿子和1个女儿的父母。他在英国英格兰戴文被列为lord of the manors of west polworth, paveston and karry。他去世于1303年在他的家乡享年73岁。"},"hr":{"1230–1303":"1230.–1303.","1240–1273":"1240–1273.","1260–Female":"1260–preminula","1270–1304":"1270.–1304","1272–Male":"1272.–preminuo","1273–Male":"1273.–preminuo","1200–1290":"1200–1290.","1210–1231":"1210–1231","1231":"1231","1230":"1230.","1273":"1273.","1240":"1240","1272":"1272.","1260":"1260","1270":"1270.","1290":"1290.","ABT 1260":"oko 1260.","1304":"1304","1303":"1303.","1259":"1259","1200":"1200","1210":"1210","about 1231":"oko 1231.","Somerset, England":"Somerset, Engleska, United Kingdom","Castle Cary,,,England":"Castle Cary, Somerset, Engleska, United Kingdom","England":"England","Castle Cary, Somersetshire, England":"Castle Cary, Somerset, England","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"cs":{"1230–1303":"1230–1303","1240–1273":"1240–1273","1260–Female":"1260–Zesnulá","1270–1304":"12